# Drafts Folder

This folder contains work-in-progress content.

## How to Use

Place your content drafts here:
- Newsletter drafts
- Article drafts
- Social media content batches
- Email sequence drafts

Claude will reference these when creating related content or repurposing.

## Naming Convention

Suggested format: `YYYY-MM-DD_content-type_topic.md`

Examples:
- 2025-01-15_newsletter_ai-writing-systems.md
- 2025-01-20_linkedin-posts_batch.md
- 2025-01-22_twitter-thread_lessons-learned.md
